                    <p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">Le désir de RREACH est de rendre le coût de la participation au Congrès abordable pour les formateurs de pasteurs qualifiés. Parce que les délégués doivent supporter leurs frais de voyage, et avec le potentiel d’inflation dans le monde entier, RREACH cherche à collecter des fonds, et espère subventionner généreusement le prix pour </span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:italic;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">tous ceux</span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;"> qui assistent au Congrès </span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;-webkit-text-decoration-skip:none;text-decoration-skip-ink:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">avec des réductions importantes et / ou des bourses</span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">. Après l’examen des facteurs socio-économiques nationaux, les frais de participation au Congrès ont été établies par pays. Veuillez noter que </span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:italic;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">les frais d’inscription de chacun</span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;"> sont </span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;-webkit-text-decoration-skip:none;text-decoration-skip-ink:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">inférieurs</span><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;"> au coût total par délégué pour assister au Congrès. RREACH ne cherche pas à recouvrir nos coûts par les frais d’inscription.</span></p><p><b style="font-weight:normal;" id="docs-internal-guid-d9d19500-7fff-adff-ded8-a54115dd48e3"><br></b></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">RREACH offre une grande valeur aux délégués qui assistent au Congrès. Selon le pays d’où vous venez, vos frais d’inscription peuvent être inférieurs au coût d’un séjour de deux nuits à l’hôtel - mais vous recevez beaucoup plus que cela en retour !&nbsp;</span></p><p><b style="font-weight:normal;"><br></b></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">Vos frais d’inscription comprennent :</span></p><p><b style="font-weight:normal;"><br></b></p><ol style="margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;padding-inline-start:48px;"><li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type:decimal;font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;margin-left: -18pt;padding-left: 18pt;" aria-level="1"><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;" role="presentation"><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">Admission de 6 jours à tous les programmes et événements du Congrès ;</span></p></li><li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type:decimal;font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;margin-left: -18pt;padding-left: 18pt;" aria-level="1"><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;" role="presentation"><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">Hébergement partagé pour 5 nuits à l’hôtel Westin Playa Bonita Panama ;</span></p></li><li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type:decimal;font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;margin-left: -18pt;padding-left: 18pt;" aria-level="1"><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;" role="presentation"><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">Tous les repas, collations et boissons non alcoolisées pendant le Congrès ;</span></p></li><li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type:decimal;font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;margin-left: -18pt;padding-left: 18pt;" aria-level="1"><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;" role="presentation"><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">Transport entre l’aéroport et l’hôtel les 11, 12, 17 et 18 novembre ;&nbsp;</span></p></li><li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type:decimal;font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;margin-left: -18pt;padding-left: 18pt;" aria-level="1"><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;" role="presentation"><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">Traduction disponible en Français, Portugais et Espagnol ; et</span></p></li><li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type:decimal;font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;margin-left: -18pt;padding-left: 18pt;" aria-level="1"><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;" role="presentation"><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">Documents imprimés et numériques du GProCongrès II.</span></p></li></ol><p><b style="font-weight:normal;"><br></b></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">Vos frais d’inscription N’INCLUENT PAS :</span></p><p><br></p><ol style="margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;padding-inline-start:48px;"><li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type:decimal;font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;margin-left: -18pt;padding-left: 18pt;" aria-level="1"><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;" role="presentation"><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">Le billet d’avion aller-retour vers/depuis Panama City ; ou</span></p></li><li dir="ltr" style="list-style-type:decimal;font-size:12pt;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;margin-left: -18pt;padding-left: 18pt;" aria-level="1"><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;" role="presentation"><span style="font-size:12pt;font-family:'Times New Roman';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">Tous les frais de passeport et/ou de visa que vous encourez en lien avec votre venue au Congrès.</span></p></li></ol> 
                @else
                    <p style="margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: Antonio; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: normal;">RREACH’s desire is to make the cost of attending the Congress affordable for qualified pastor trainers. Because delegates have to bear their travel costs, and with the potential for inflation worldwide, RREACH seeks to raise funds, and hopes to generously subsidize the price for all who attend the Congress with significant discounts and/or scholarships. After considering national socio-economic factors, fees for the Congress have been established per country.&nbsp;<span style="color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-color: transparent;">Please note that everyone’s registration fees are less than the total cost per delegate to attend the Congress. RREACH is not attempting to recover our costs from the registration fees.</span></p><p style="margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: Antonio; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: normal;"><span style="color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-color: transparent;"><br></span></p><p style="margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: Antonio; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: normal;">RREACH is offering great value for delegates who attend the Congress. Depending on which country you are coming from, your registration fee may be less than the cost of a two-night stay at the hotel – but you receive much more than that in return! </p><p style="margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: Antonio; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: normal;"><br></p><p style="margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: Antonio; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: normal;">Your registration fee includes:</p><p style="margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: Antonio; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: normal;">1. 6-day admission to all programs and events at the Congress;</p><p style="margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: Antonio; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: normal;">2. Twin-sharing accommodations for 5 nights at the Westin Playa Bonita Panama Hotel;</p><p style="margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: Antonio; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: normal;">3. All meals, snacks, and non-alcoholic beverages during the Congress;</p><p style="margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: Antonio; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: normal;">4. Transportation between the airport and the hotel on November 11, 12, 17 and 18;</p><p style="margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: Antonio; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: normal;">5. Translation available in French, Portuguese, and Spanish; and</p><p style="margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: Antonio; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: normal;">6. GProCongress II printed and digital materials.</p><p style="margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: Antonio; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: normal;"><br></p><p style="margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: Antonio; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: normal;">Your registration fee DOES NOT include:</p><p style="margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: Antonio; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: normal;">1. Round-trip airfare to/from Panama City; or</p><p style="margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: Antonio; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: normal;">2. Any passport and/or visa fees you incur in connection with coming to the Congress.</p>
